<!-- FAQ -->
<section class="faq-sec">
  <span class="section-label">Support</span>
  <h2 class="section-h2">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
  <div class="faq-grid">
    <div class="faq-item">
      <div class="faq-q">Which apps are these brushes compatible with?</div>
      <p class="faq-a">The Flare Pack is currently built for <strong style="color:var(--white)">Procreate on iPad</strong>. It works on all iPad models running Procreate 5 and above. A Photoshop version is currently in development. Join the mailing list to be notified on release.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-item">
      <div class="faq-q">How do I install the brushes in Procreate?</div>
      <p class="faq-a">A full PDF installation guide is included with every purchase. The short version: download the ZIP, unzip it on your iPad, tap the .brushset file, and Procreate opens it automatically. Your brushes appear instantly in your brush library.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-item">
      <div class="faq-q">I didn't receive my download email &mdash; what now?</div>
      <p class="faq-a">Check your spam or junk folder first. If it's not there, log into your account at <a href="https://lacquerbru.co.za/my-account">lacquerbru.co.za/my-account</a> and access your downloads from there. Still stuck? Email us at <a href="mailto:howzit@lacquerbru.co.za">howzit@lacquerbru.co.za</a> and we'll sort it out quickly.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-item">
      <div class="faq-q">How many times can I download my purchase?</div>
      <p class="faq-a">Each purchase allows <strong style="color:var(--white)">3 download attempts</strong> within a <strong style="color:var(--white)">14-day window</strong>. If you need additional access after this period, contact us and we will assist you.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-item">
      <div class="faq-q">Can I get a refund on a digital product?</div>
      <p class="faq-a">Due to the instant nature of digital delivery, we cannot offer refunds once a file has been downloaded. If you experience a technical issue that prevents you from using the pack, contact us and we will find a solution.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-item">
      <div class="faq-q">Will I get free updates when the pack is improved?</div>
      <p class="faq-a">Yes. If you purchased from <strong style="color:var(--white)">lacquerbru.co.za</strong> you will receive an email with a new download link whenever the pack is updated. Your purchase covers all future versions of the same pack.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

